{"tid":938921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（突發）光明會紙牌tax reform恐成真","createTime":"2018-12-12T16:42:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-13T02:28:22.000Z","uid":130174,"like":23,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"051023bd80988fcaaa0eabe071027f8d233c469e","tid":938921,"uid":130174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T16:42:07.000Z","msg":"依張係光明會紙牌<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k8hDUsn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk8hDUsn.jpg&h=d09c4e50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「稅制改革」<br />\n<br />\n稅制的改革，就是老百姓們的斷頭台<br />\n<br />\n卡片下方寫著：<br />\n<br />\n&quot;換句話說，就是『增稅』<br />\n<br />\n當它們擁有你的錢包時，政府才會甘心把手拿出你的口袋&quot;<br />\n<br />\n睇埋黃背心運動<br />\n維基百科<br />\n示威者起初因為不滿油價持續上揚以及馬克龍政府調高燃油稅而上街抗議，但是訴求迅速擴大到其他如提升草根及中產階級的購買力以及要求法國總統馬克龍下台等。<br />\n<br />\n有人為馬克龍整左斷頭台<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.sina.cn/gj/2018-12-11/detail-ihmutuec8007988.d.html?from=wap\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sina.cn%2Fgj%2F2018-12-11%2Fdetail-ihmutuec8007988.d.html%3Ffrom%3Dwap&d=pNmjKUHxl5ctTJihngLYQ8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=c25f8d66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.sina.cn/gj/2018-12-11/detail-ihmutuec8007988.d.html?from=wap</a> 殘體報道<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ynJ0onX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FynJ0onX.jpg&h=2522d706&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hupVWHY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhupVWHY.jpg&h=8d4ba800&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DCqaLBm.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDCqaLBm.gif&h=75874db9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdc5ad5230e80df92a32879f37e6d6be816d7c4b","tid":938921,"uid":65354,"like":25,"